
## TRUNK LID REMOVAL/INSTALLATION  


## Warning  


Warning- Removing the balance spring without supporting the trunk lid can be dangerous. The trunk lid may fall and injure you. Open the trunk lid fully and support it before removing the balance spring. Perform these procedures together with another person.  


1. Disconnect the negative battery cable. 
2. Remove the rear package trim. (Refer to 09-17 REAR PACKAGE TRIM REMOVAL/INSTALLATION.) 
3. Remove in the order indicated in the table. 
4. Install in the reverse order of removal. 
5. Adjust the trunk lid. (Refer to 09-10 TRUNK LID ADJUSTMENT.)  

